# SESSION PROTOCOL

## ON SESSION START (MANDATORY)

**STOP. Execute these before any work:**

### 1. Read current state
```bash
cat doc/agent/sketch.md
```

### 2. Check branch and recent history
```bash
git branch --show-current
git log --oneline -10 --show-notes --all
```

### 3. Check latest idea version
```bash
ls -t doc/agent/idea_versions/ | head -1 | xargs -I{} cat doc/agent/idea_versions/{}
```

### 4. State your understanding aloud
> "Phase: ___. Current idea version: ___. Last action: ___. Next step: ___."

### 5. If unclear → ASK USER. If clear → proceed.

