## CONTEXT UPDATE TRIGGERS

| When | Update What |
|------|-------------|
| After survey finds papers | survey_cache.md (append papers) |
| After validating an idea | idea_versions/v\<N\>.md + sketch.md |
| After evaluating a direction | directions/dir_\<name\>.md + sketch.md |
| After direction decision | decisions.md + sketch.md |
| After insight/pattern found | findings.md |
| Before risky pivot | `git commit` + sketch.md |
| At session end | sketch.md (full state) + `git add doc/agent/ && git commit` |

**Heuristic: If session crashes now, would the next session know what happened?**
- No → update context now
- Yes → keep working

