# PAPER DISCOVERY & READING

Use methods from `/paper_related_works` and `/topic_survey` for all paper operations.

**Discover papers:**
- Semantic Scholar API: keyword search (`/paper/search?query=...`) + citation graph (`/paper/ArXiv:{ID}?fields=citations...`)
- Web search: `site:arxiv.org`, `site:paperswithcode.com`
- Citation chains from papers already in survey cache
- For key papers: run `/paper_related_works` logic to map predecessors + successors

**Read papers** via AlphaXiv (always try first for any arXiv paper):
```
WebFetch: https://alphaxiv.org/overview/{PAPER_ID}.md    # structured overview
WebFetch: https://alphaxiv.org/abs/{PAPER_ID}.md         # full text fallback
```

